     ("Pumice floats on water because:",["It's made of ice","*It's full of gas bubbles (vesicles) making its overall density less than water","It's hollow","It's a mineral"],"Pumice property."),
     ("The rock cycle shows that:",["Rocks never change","Only igneous rocks exist","*Any rock type can be transformed into any other type given the right conditions","Metamorphic rocks are oldest"],"Cycle principle."),
     ("Quartzite forms from the metamorphism of:",["Limestone","Shale","*Sandstone (quartz sand recrystallizes into interlocking quartz grains)","Basalt"],"Quartzite origin."),
