     ("Erosion differs from weathering because erosion involves:",["No water","Chemical change only","*Transport of weathered material by water, wind, ice, or gravity","Only temperature changes"],"Erosion vs. weathering."),
     ("Sedimentary rocks are important because they:",["Are the hardest","Never contain fossils","*Often contain fossils and record Earth's surface history","Are the most common deep underground"],"Sedimentary significance."),
