    "<li><b>Cinder Cone:</b> Smallest; steep sides; explosive fragments (Parícutin).</li>"
    "<li><b>Composite (Stratovolcano):</b> Tall, steep; alternating lava/ash layers; explosive (Mt. St. Helens, Fuji).</li></ul>"
